        "scope": "Other: Covers council services and wholly owned companies",
        "sectors": "Other: The plan is currently in the draft stages, with the aim of publishing within 2024. All targets will be reviewed a year after publication to track the success of our adaptive efforts, with updates being assessed through this.|Monitoring: Information on progress of plan is monitored and publicly reported every 1-3 years",
