        "sector": "Stationary energy: Energy efficiency/ retrofit measures addressing existing commercial, residential and/or municipal buildings",
        "description": "The Council is embarking on a programme of work, underpinned by and Asset Management and Decarbonisation Plan, to get the Council's buildings to net zero carbon.",
        "status": "2024",
        "cobenefits": "2045",
        "financeStatus": "Estimated reduction in annual inventory emissions due to action|Estimated annual energy savings due to action",
