        "planType": "Integrated climate plan (addressing mitigation, adaptation and energy-related issues)",
        "planName": "Climate Ready Leicester Plan (2023-2028)\\n\\nhttps://www.leicester.gov.uk/media/jtzb0omp/climate-ready-leicester-plan-2023-28.pdf",
        "yearAdopted": null,
