        "sectors": "Monitoring: Information on progress of plan is monitored and publicly reported annually or more frequently than annually|Evaluation: Evaluation of plan takes place annually or more frequently than annually|Update: Updates to the plan are published every 1-3 years",
        "renewableTarget": "The city's overall goal of achieving carbon neutrality takes account of the Tyndall Centre pathway for limiting heating to 1.5\u00b0C. This has also fed in to the Roadmap which has been developed for net zero in the city, which will form the basis of future action plans. The Roadmap itself models four different decarbonisation scenarios, which will be used as the basis for future action planning.",
