        "description": "Cornwall and Isles of Scilly Climate Commission: An independent group established for Cornwall and the Isles of Scilly. The Commission will report to the Cornwall and Isles of Scilly Leadership Board and will seek to challenge, catalyse and convene the region's leaders, organisations and communities to take effective action in the face of the climate and ecological emergencies. Developed between Cornwall Council with the University of Exeter and Place Based Climate Action Network (PCAN) (https://pcancities.org.uk). The Climate Commission will work across sectors (public, private and voluntary) and include a wide range of climate expertise and knowledge. https://cornwallandiosclimate.org.uk/",
