        "description": "Cornwall and Isles of Scilly Leadership Board is a group of leaders from key organisations across Cornwall which meets to ensure co-ordination across many different policy and strategy areas - including climate change. https://www.cornwall.gov.uk/the-council-and-democracy/cornwall-and-isles-of-scilly-leadership-board/",
