        "focusAreas": "Forestry|Natural environment|Resilience|Agriculture|Food|Adaptation",
        "description": "Royal Cornwall Show 2025 - The Local Nature Partnership for Cornwall and the Isles of Scilly hosted an award winning Farming, Food and Nature Hub, bringing together a range of exhibitors including Cornwall Council Nature Recovery, Forest for Cornwall, Local Investment in Nature Cornwall, Cornwall Wildlife Trust, the National Trust and Westcountry Rivers Trust. The Hub promoted regenerative agriculture by bringing together key organisations to engage the community and highlight the support available. The show is held over three days and attracts thousands of visitors, so is a key engagement opportunity for key sectors as well as residents and the wider community. ",
        "otherEntities": "NGO and associations|Agriculture|Climate initiatives/networks"
