        "focusAreas": "Finance|Emissions reduction",
        "description": "To understand how other peer cities are approaching the challenge of decarbonising Council officers have been investigating how other UK local authorities intend to fund their climate action plans and have been linking with UK cities such as Bristol City Council and the Greater London Authority where partnerships climate funds with multi-million pound profiles have been formed between public and private sectors.",
