        "focusAreas": "Industry",
        "description": "The Circular Glasgow Network is an initiative of the Glasgow Chamber of Commerce supported by Zero Waste Scotland and Glasgow City Council with the aim to connect support and inspire businesses of all sizes to innovate and adopt circular strategies. It supports businesses across the city to connect and share ideas on climate action and helps build knowledge of how a circular economy supports business growth and the city's climate ambitions. Circular Glasgow delivers a programme of business engagement highlighting opportunities of the circular economy.(https://www.circularglasgow.com/).",
