        "description": "To secure an affordable, low carbon energy supply for London we need to make greater use of local energy resources. The Mayor's policies on new development alone are helping to deliver CO2 emission reductions. In 2024 applications considered by the Mayor achieved CO2 emission reductions of 56 per cent above national Building Regulations; comfortably surpassing the London Plan minimum target of 35 per cent. This is estimated to save over 33,105 tonnes CO2 per annum and approximately \u00a316 million in solar PV panels as well as additional investment in energy efficiency measures and technologies such as heat pumps and connections to district heating networks. Monitoring report: https://www.london.gov.uk/programmes-strategies/planning/implementing-london-plan/energy-monitoring-reports",
