        "comment": "The Local Energy Market development programme has engaged across different levels of government to work towards the projects goals of creating a smart energy system. The programme encompasses three key components 1) Local Area Energy Planning2) Development of new smart energy tariffs 3) Development of local energy trading platform Development of all three informs national regulation, legislation and policy, and supports the local area to accelerate deployment of climate mitigating measures and the optimisation of the measures afterwards. Local Area Energy Plans have been created for each of the 10 Local Authorities within GM. "
