        "description": "Since 2018 GMCA has put on an annual Greater Manchester Green Summit. This brings together cross-sectoral stakeholders to watch panels, take part in workshops and network. The event focuses on showcasing progress as well as discussing the difficult challenges in tackling climate change. Each year the event aims to expand the audience and engage and collaborate with a greater number of stakeholders. The events have focused on bringing in more community groups, engaging with young people and attracting business leaders. ",
