        "renewableTarget": "The Climate Change Action Plan (CCAP) has been informed by the Climate Change Risk and Vulnerability Assessment, which utilised UKCP18 data for Kirklees, using RCP8.5 scenario at current, 2030, 2050 and 2080 timeframes. The (CCAP) outlines our approach of how the district of Kirklees can achieve its ambition to be 'Net Zero and Climate Ready by 2038'. Furthermore, the Net Zero Assessment for the district (also found on our Climate Emergency webpage) utilises three different action scenarios to show a pathway to net zero by 2038, which are cost-effective, cost-neutral and technologically possible.",
