        "renewableTarget": "The Lake District National Park Climate Change Adaptation Report 2021 was used to describe climate scenarios. Regional data taken from UK Climate Projections 18 (UKCP18) was used to forecast how a number of climatic variables will change in the National Park over the short (2030), medium (2050) and long term 2080). UKCP18 is the latest data available in the freely climate analysis tool from the Met Office's Hadley Centre Climate Programme.",
