        "description": "We ran a Citizens' Assembly on the climate crisis with 50 residents to develop a Climate Action plan. This plan identifies five priority areas (adaptation, buildings and energy, transport, waste, consumption and food and biodiversity and environmental quality) with 20 goals that set out how we will take climate action. \\nThrough this work, we collaborated with our Partnership's founding members, such as hospitals, universities, schools, businesses, culture venues and housing associations. ",
