        "description": "Over last year, the Lambeth Climate Partnership (LCP) received an innovation grant to research how best to collaborate and connect dots locally (Innovate UK - an arm of UK Research and Innovation).\\n\\nAs part of this, the LCP has opened its membership to the public and now has access to a network of over 2,800 local organisations, covering public, private and third sectors.\\n\\nThe LCP has spent last year on experimentation for facilitation and has found the most prolific areas to be knowledge exchange (talks with over 190 in person attendees) and networking (which has led to successful funding applications for green innovation of \u00a3100k). \\n\\nLCP is continuing activities for 2025/26 for networking, learning and attracting funding.\\n",
