        "refId": "Mitigation Action 10",
        "sector": "Transportation: Improve bus infrastructure, services, and operations",
        "description": "In 2022, the North East published the Bus Service Improvement Plan (BSIP) which sets out a wide range of significant proposed improvements to every aspect of bus services that will be delivered through a formal Partnership of bus operators, the NEJTC, Local Authorities and Nexus. The key objectives include the reduction of carbon emissions, improvements in air quality, the growth of our economy and the advancement of the health and wellbeing of local people through the increased use of sustainable forms of transport. Here is the link to the most recent version of the North East BSIP: file:///C:/Users/92452/AppData/Local/Temp/MicrosoftEdgeDownloads/a18859f0-f1ad-4352-91e2-f93af1b62515/BSIP-Refresh-Sept-23.pdf",
