        "sector": "Other, please specify: Other: Organisational emissions (including Scope 1, 2 and 3)",
        "description": "Newcastle City Council conducted an in-depth data collection and analysis of the council's scope 1, 2 and 3 carbon emissions - this included looking at all scope 3 categories as defined by the Greenhouse Gas Protocol. The project means that Newcastle is now one of the leading local authorities in this area of work and are the first council to explore emissions such as those resulting from city events and the first to incorporate emissions from a comprehensive set our leased assets into the council's emission baseline. This analysis will allow the council to identify and prioritise mitigation actions throughout the organisation.",
