        "description": "Boulby Potash Mine (ICL) S106 Agreement for peatland restoration. \\n\\n\u00a31.5 million of investment (over 10 years) was negotiated as part of the Boubly Potash Mine (ICL) S106 Agreement required by a recent planning approval for an extension to the mine's operation.\\n\\nFirst 3 years of scheduled payments have been used as much funding for peatland restoration projects in the Park (providing private mathc to Natural England Nature for Climate Restoration funding).",
