        "comment": "PSB has been undertaking a climate risk and vulnerability assessment including workshops with national and regional stakeholder organisations.\\n\\nThis includes statutory and invited partner bodies such as: \\nStatutory\\n\u2022\\tPowys County Council\\n\u2022\\tPowys Teaching Health Board\\n\u2022\\tNatural Resources Wales\\n\u2022\\tMid and West Wales Fire and Rescue Service\\nInvited participants\\n\u2022\\tBannau Brycheiniog National Park Authority\\n\u2022\\tPAVO\\n\u2022\\tDyfed Powys Police\\n\u2022\\tOffice of the Dyfed-Powys Police and Crime Commissioner\\n\u2022\\tHM Prisons and Probation Service\\n\u2022\\tWelsh Government\\n\\nIn addition collaboration has been undertaken with a range of representative, third sector and utility bodies such as;\\n- Dwr Cymru (Welsh Water)\\n- NFU (National Farming Union \\n- National Grid \\n"
