        "impacts": "Increased and heavy precipitation events can have drastic effects on urbanised populations. Drainage and sewerage systems are ill equipped in the borough to deal with significant downpours, leading to localised flooding and displacement of people and communities. Financial damages associated with costs from flood damage will impact businesses and communities, particularly those in low income households. An increase of flood events may also lead to damages to health assets, impacting on the public's access to health and social care services.",
