        "sector": "Stationary energy: On-site renewable energy generation",
        "description": "Solar Together is a group buying scheme for solar panels in Surrey. Since it began, there have been 2885 installations, with 13.67MW of renewable capacity installed and a carbon reduction of 2721tCO2e, and a bill saving of \u00a33.77M annually for residents.",
