        "sector": "Stationary energy: Energy efficiency/ retrofit measures addressing existing commercial, residential and/or municipal buildings",
        "description": "The Council was successful in winning significant Public Sector Decarbonisation Scheme (PSDS) grant funding to enable effective whole-building decarbonisation on several buildings, including the replacement of low carbon heating, insulation, as well as the installation of solar PV on roofs and in car parks. So far, 15 buildings have had heat pumps installed, and 8 of these have been fully retrofitted. This has saved 1000tCO2e annually, and has resulted in a bill saving of \u00a30.92M annually.",
